Genesis Energy, L.P. To Present At MLPA Investor Conference

        
        Genesis Energy, L.P.






Business Wire




May 31, 2017 6:30 AM EDT



 













































  Genesis Energy, L.P. (NYSE:GEL) announced today that Grant E. Sims, CEO, will make a scheduled presentation at 2017 MLP Investor Conference sponsored by the Master Limited Partnership Association (MLPA) and meet with investors throughout the conference. The conference is being held in Orlando, FL on May 31 through June 2, 2017. Mr. Sims' presentation will begin at 4:40 p.m. (EDT) on Wednesday, May 31, 2017.  The Partnership's latest presentation materials are available and may be downloaded by visiting the Partnership's website at www.genesisenergy.com under "Presentations" under the Investors tab.  Genesis Energy, L.P. is a diversified midstream energy master limited partnership headquartered in Houston, Texas. Genesis' operations include offshore pipeline transportation, refinery services, marine transportation and supply and logistics. Genesis' operations are primarily located in Texas, Louisiana, Arkansas, Mississippi, Alabama, Florida, Wyoming and the Gulf of Mexico.      View source version on businesswire.com:   http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170531005419/en/  



 
 
























